00:54:01.869 --> 00:54:09.220
of whether marriage for you and for this particular
person you're considering marrying, whether

00:54:09.220 --> 00:54:17.510
that is right for you is an individual decision
that you need to make carefully, slowly and

00:54:17.510 --> 00:54:20.430
